@startuml UseCaseDiagram
title Appointment Reservation System - Use Case Diagram

left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

actor Guest as guest
actor "Registered User" as user
actor Administrator as admin

rectangle "Appointment Reservation System" {

  package "Authentication" {
    usecase "Register Account" as UC_Register
    usecase "Login" as UC_Login
    usecase "Logout" as UC_Logout
    usecase "View Current Session" as UC_Me
  }

  package "User Features" {
    usecase "View Available Services" as UC_ViewServices
    usecase "View Appointment Slots" as UC_ViewSlots
    usecase "Create Appointment Reservation" as UC_CreateReservation
    usecase "Cancel Reservation" as UC_CancelReservation
    usecase "View Reservation History" as UC_ViewHistory
    usecase "View User Profile" as UC_Profile
  }

  package "Administrator Features" {
    usecase "Create Service" as UC_CreateService
    usecase "Edit Service" as UC_EditService
    usecase "Delete Service" as UC_DeleteService
    usecase "Create Appointment Slot" as UC_CreateSlot
    usecase "Delete Appointment Slot" as UC_DeleteSlot
    usecase "View All Reservations" as UC_ViewAllReservations
    usecase "Manage Users" as UC_ManageUsers
  }
}

' Guest
guest --> UC_Register
guest --> UC_Login
guest --> UC_ViewServices
guest --> UC_ViewSlots

' Registered User
user --> UC_Login
user --> UC_Logout
user --> UC_Me
user --> UC_ViewServices
user --> UC_ViewSlots
user --> UC_CreateReservation
user --> UC_CancelReservation
user --> UC_ViewHistory
user --> UC_Profile

' Administrator inherits user capabilities
admin -|> user
admin --> UC_CreateService
admin --> UC_EditService
admin --> UC_DeleteService
admin --> UC_CreateSlot
admin --> UC_DeleteSlot
admin --> UC_ViewAllReservations
admin --> UC_ManageUsers

' Include / Extend relationships
UC_CreateReservation ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_CancelReservation ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_ViewHistory ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_Profile ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_CreateService ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_EditService ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_DeleteService ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_CreateSlot ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_DeleteSlot ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_ViewAllReservations ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_ManageUsers ..> UC_Login : <<include>>

note right of UC_CreateReservation
  Business rules enforced:
  - Slot must exist and be available
  - Slot cannot be in the past
  - No duplicate active reservation
  - Slot marked unavailable on success
end note

@enduml
